The landing page extensively uses InsureCo design tokens:

### Colors
- `--interactive-primary`: Brand red for buttons and accents
- `--background-primary`: Main background
- `--background-secondary`: Alternate section backgrounds
- `--text-primary`: Main text color
- `--text-secondary`: Supporting text color
- `--text-on-color`: White text on colored backgrounds
- `--color-success`: Checkmark icons

### Spacing
- `--spacing-03` through `--spacing-13`: Component spacing
