### Motion
- `--motion-hover`: Button and tile hover transitions
- Smooth scroll behavior for anchor links

## Responsive Design

### Mobile (< 672px)
- Hero heading size reduced
- CTA buttons stack vertically
- Product sections reflow to single column
- Reduced padding and minimum heights

### Tablet (672px - 1056px)
- Two-column layouts for some sections
- Adjusted image placeholder sizes

### Desktop (> 1056px)
- Full multi-column layouts
- Maximum width containers
- Larger hero section

